                                <support>
                                    <p><material>Parchment and paper</material>.</p>
                                </support>
                                <extent>7, fols 1v, 2v, 3v are blank. Fol. 1 which is of parchment
                                    has been folded and therefore its real length is 277 mm. The
                                    length of fol. 2 is 135 mm. While the first two folios are
                                    parchment and from the fourteenth century, the last three paper
                                    leaves are from sixteenth century and are written by Árni
                                        Magnússon.<dimensions type="leaf" scope="all">
                                        <height unit="mm">210</height>
                                        <width unit="mm">170</width>
                                    </dimensions>
                                </extent>
                            </supportDesc>
                        </objectDesc>
